      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## What the class supplies\n\nThe canonical `node` class gives a created instance:\n\n- a starter label\n- a starter size\n- starter data fields like `title`, `body`, and `status`\n- authored views such as detail, summary, icon, and editor\n\nThe instance still belongs to the current graph. After creation, edit the local node like any other node.",
        "identity": {
          "graphId": "node-class-demo-declaration"
        },
        "_placement": {
          "version": 1,
